data.description: **MOTIVATED SELLER NOW OFFERING the $5,000 CREDIT TO HELP BUYER WITH CLOSING COST!**Location, Location! Welcome to this cozy and well-loved 3 bedroom, 1 bath home by Lake Loveland! Endless potential throughout and move-in ready! Upon entering, Buyers will love the abundance of natural light and functional flow of the home with a large living room, formal dining room and a cute "breakfast nook" or coffee bar as you enter the kitchen. New oven and some updates to the kitchen with freshly painted cabinets and a new laminate countertop and vinyl-tile flooring. The walk-through laundry room boasts ample storage and cabinet space and the washer/dryer is included. 3 bedrooms and full bath all down the hall but the upstairs 3rd bedrooms is unique and must see to appreciate the bonus oversized 2nd closet that could be used for so much possibilities. Large fenced back yard and a quiet neighborhood with incredible walkability! A short walk to the swim beach at the lake, the sculpture garden, shops, restaurants, and schools! Seller added brand new 3/4' gas line and on-demand tankless water heater. Close to several other amenities like parks and golf course, don't miss out on this incredible opportunity. Book your showings today!
